    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 remains a benchmark of longitudinal front-engine, rear-drive dynamics. Powered by the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, the powerplant delivers linear throttle response through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis features a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the suspension retains its factory-spec geometry for precise turn-in. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a recent valve shim adjustment and cooling system overhaul.",
