      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though closer inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well, both consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats show only light bolster wear, and every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent idle, backed by a comprehensive service history including a recent synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the tires have ample tread remaining on uncurbed alloy wheels. This is a non-smoker, pet-free car that has been primarily garaged, offering the next owner a reliable and sophisticated driving experience that truly stands out in its class.",
